headline: International Paper to Release First-Quarter Earnings on April 30, 2025
summary: International Paper (NYSE: IP; LSE: IPC), the global leader in sustainable packaging solutions, will release first-quarter earnings on April 30, 2025, before the opening of the New York Stock Exchange.
